!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Use of Information</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may use information about you for various purposes, including to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Search and display code snippets to your and other’s code related searches.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Provide, operate, maintain, improve and promote the Website and Services to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Monitor and analyse trends, usage and activities in connection with the Services for marketing and advertising purposes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Provide customer support services to you, respond to your questions and requests, send you technical or administrative updates and messages.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Providing your personal data to others</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We do not share or disclose your personal data or content with any third parties, except as provided under this Policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Website and the Services may contain links to other websites, whose privacy practices may differ from our own. If you submit your personal data to any third-party website, your data is governed by their privacy policies. Therefore we ask you to carefully read the privacy statements of any website you visit and consider submitting personal data to.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may disclose your data (including your personal data) to third parties if such disclosure is reasonably necessary for the purpose of:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Complying with applicable laws, regulations, court orders, legal processes or governmental requests.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Preventing harmful or illegal activities and, in urgent circumstances, protecting the personal safety of Grepper, our customers and the public</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Protecting the security and integrity of the Services and defending the rights or property of Grepper.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Where reasonable, for maintaining, updating or otherwise implementing our data security measures, equipment, technical operations and the like.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may display on the Website testimonials of customer of Grepper, who are satisfied with our Services. With your explicit consent and confirmation we may post your personal testimonial or our Website too, along with your name.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may transfer your data (including personal data) in connection with or in the process of negotiating the sale, assignment, or other transfer of the Grepper business or any part thereof, or as part of a security audit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Sharing Aggregate &amp; Anonymised Data</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may also share aggregated or anonymised data that does not directly identify you or any of your personal data to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Provide, operate, maintain, improve and promote the Website and Services to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Provide customer support services to you, respond to your questions and requests, send you technical or administrative updates and messages</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Monitor and analyse trends, usage and activities in connection with the Services for marketing and advertising purposes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Provide advanced aggregated anonymised analyses</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Storing and protecting your data</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Grepper takes reasonable steps to ensure that all personal data we collect is transferred and stored in a secure manner. In doing so we make sure, as far as reasonably possible, that the collected and stored personal data is protected from misuse, interference, unauthorised access, modification or disclosure. We do so by means of using verified methods including access limitation, industry-standard Transport Layer Security (TLS) encryption technology to safeguard sensitive information, data encryption, and firewalls.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Data collected by Grepper may be stored and processed in the United States. We uphold and maintain strict procedures for protecting data stored in our servers and access is limited to those employees whose work-related duties involve working with such data. You acknowledge and agree that by providing personal data to Grepper you consent to the transmission of data (including personal data) over international borders, as necessary for processing your requests.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Your Rights</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Account Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You may cancel services, update, correct or delete information about you at any time by emailing us at support@codegrepper.com, but note that we may retain certain information as required by law or for legitimate business purposes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Cookies</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Most web browsers are set to accept cookies by default. If you prefer, you can usually choose to set your browser to remove or reject browser cookies. Removing or rejecting browser cookies does not necessarily affect third party flash cookies used in connection with our Services. To delete or disable flash cookies please visit http://helpx.adobe.com/flash-player/kb/disable-local-shared-objects-flash.html for more information. Please note that if you choose to remove or reject cookies, this could affect the availability and functionality of our Services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Contact Us</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: support@codegrepper.com.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Grepper Privacy Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-06-23 14:46:34', '2022-06-23 14:46:34', '', 3, 'http://localhost/booking/?p=71', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
